400 inline void OnboardNodeHandler::storeMeasurements()
401 {
402  systemid_thread_mutex.lock();
403  if(systemid_flag_)
404  {
405  systemid_thread_mutex.unlock();

407  }
408  systemid_thread_mutex.unlock();
409

411  //ROS_INFO("Time: %f, delay_send_time: %f, systemid_size: %d",time, delay_send_time_, systemid_measurements.size());
412  if(time >= delay_send_time_ && meas_filled_< systemid_measurements.size())
413  {
414  //Set initial state for the first time:
415  if(meas_filled_ == 0)
416  {
417  setInitialState();//Set Initial State for SystemID
418  //Print the current State:
419  /*cout<<"Pos: "<<systemid_init_state.p.transpose()<<endl;
420  cout<<"Vel: "<<systemid_init_state.v.transpose()<<endl;
421  cout<<"R: "<<endl<<systemid_init_state.R<<endl;
422  cout<<"w: "<<systemid_init_state.w.transpose()<<endl;
423  cout<<"u: "<<systemid_init_state.u.transpose()<<endl;
424  */
425  }
426  QRotorSystemIDMeasurement &prev_meas = systemid_measurements[meas_filled_];
427  prev_meas.position<<data.localpos.x, data.localpos.y, data.localpos.z;
428  prev_meas.rpy<<data.rpydata.x, data.rpydata.y, data.rpydata.z;
429  meas_filled_++;
430  //ROS_INFO("Meas Filled: %d, Size: %d",meas_filled_, systemid_measurements.size());
431  }
432 
433  if(time <= measurement_period - delay_send_time_)
434  {
435  if(control_measurements.size() > 0)//not empty
436  {
437  QRotorSystemIDMeasurement measurement;
438  measurement.t = time;
439  double time_diff = measurement.t - prev_ctrl_time;
440  if(time_diff < 0.005)
441  {
442  ROS_WARN("Time diff Expected 0.02; Found: %f, size: %lu, time: %f; skipping measurement",time_diff, control_measurements.size(), time);
443  if(meas_filled_ > 0)
444  --meas_filled_;
445  return;
446  //time_diff = time_diff < 0.005?0.005:(time_diff > 0.025)?0.025:time_diff;//Hard reset;
447  }
448 
449  measurement.control[0] = rpytcmd.w;
450  measurement.control[1] = (rpytcmd.x - control_measurements.back()[0])/time_diff;
451  measurement.control[2] = (rpytcmd.y - control_measurements.back()[1])/time_diff;
452  measurement.control[3] = (rpytcmd.z - control_measurements.back()[2])/time_diff;
453  //Record:
454  systemid_measurements.push_back(measurement);
455  }
456  control_measurements.push_back(Vector3d(rpytcmd.x, rpytcmd.y, rpytcmd.z));
457  prev_ctrl_time = time;
458  }
459 
460  if(time >= measurement_period)
461  {
462  systemid_thread_mutex.lock();
463  systemid_flag_ = true;
464  systemid_thread_mutex.unlock();
465  }
466 }

1088 void OnboardNodeHandler::receiveGuiCommands(const rqt_quadcoptergui::GuiCommandMessage &command_msg)

1094  stateTransitionLogging(command_msg.command);
1095  break;
1096  case command_msg.enable_tracking://1
1097  stateTransitionLogging(true);
1098  stateTransitionTracking(command_msg.command);
1099  break;
1100  case command_msg.enable_vel_control://2
1101  stateTransitionVelControl(command_msg.command);
1102  break;

1104  stateTransitionRpytControl(command_msg.command);
1105  break;

1107  stateTransitionPosControl(command_msg.command);
1108  break;
1109  case command_msg.enable_mpc_control:
1110  stateTransitionMPCControl(command_msg.command);
1111  break;
1112  case command_msg.enable_trajectory_tracking:
1113  stateTransitionTrajectoryTracking(command_msg.command);
1114  break;
1115  case command_msg.enable_arm:
1116  stateTransitionEnableArm(command_msg.command);
1117  break;
1118  case command_msg.arm_quad ://6
1119  ROS_INFO("Arming Quad");
1120  armQuad();
1121  break;
1122  case command_msg.land_quad://7
1123  ROS_INFO("Landing Quad");
1124  landQuad();
1125  break;
1126  case command_msg.disarm_quad://8
1127  ROS_INFO("Disarming Quad");
1128  disarmQuad();
1129  break;

1131  ROS_INFO("Initializing MPC Trajectory");

1621 void OnboardNodeHandler::armcmdTimerCallback(const ros::TimerEvent& event)

1628  {
1629  ROS_WARN("Unable to get object position!");
1630  return;
1631  }
1632  // transform object position from camera to arm frame
1633  Eigen::Vector3d object_position_cam(object_position_cam_geo.x, object_position_cam_geo.y, object_position_cam_geo.z);
1634  Eigen::Vector3d object_position_arm = arm_cam_tf_eig_*object_position_cam;
1635  if(arm_model)
1636  {
1637  double a[2][3];
1638  double p[3] = {object_position_arm(0), 0, object_position_arm(2)};
1639 
1640  double ikres = arm_model->Ik(a, p);
1641  if(ikres > 0)//The object is within reach
1642  {
1643  arm_hardware_controller_->setJointAngles(a[0][1],a[0][2],1700);
1644  }
1645  //Check if the tip is close to the object:
1646  double angles_arm[3] = {0, (*arm_hardware_controller_)[0], (*arm_hardware_controller_)[1]};
1647  double tip_pos[3];
1648  arm_model->Fk(tip_pos, angles_arm);
1649  double error_tip_pos = pow((tip_pos[0] - p[0]),2) + pow((tip_pos[2] - p[2]),2);
1650  if(error_tip_pos < tolerance_tip_pos_)
1651  {
